{"tid":2399614,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"稅務學會建議政府寬減本年度利得稅薪俸稅及差餉","createTime":"2021-02-08T09:38:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T15:29:51.000Z","uid":54800,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3c49f15fa25ed2b7259444514e59839ad1e86fea","tid":2399614,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T09:38:16.000Z","msg":"新一份財政預算案將於本月底公布，香港稅務學會建議，政府可因應新型肺炎疫情而作出多項一次性支援，包括寬減20/21年度利得稅及薪俸稅，上限2萬元；寬減期內4個季度差餉，以每季1500元為上限；並延長分期交稅附加費至20/21課稅年度。<br />\n<br />\n學會又建議，豁免首次置業從價印花稅，樓價需為800萬以下，單位需連續3年居住，如果3年內出售要補交獲豁免的印花稅。並建議作出租金支出稅務扣減，每年10萬元。<br />\n<br />\n為提供更多誘因使用私營醫療服務，學會建議，為納稅人及其配偶及受撫養人，提供住院費用稅務扣減，上限每年10萬；並建議政府考慮提供醫保保費稅務扣減。"},{"pid":"84e8ceb404a2fa015c2c9e4341a1ed381e7da00f","tid":2399614,"uid":54800,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T09:38:49.000Z","msg":"第一次聽見有&quot;稅務學會&quot;...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc63897231df9d818b71ac2daaffb8c6b8f9030d","tid":2399614,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84e8ceb404a2fa015c2c9e4341a1ed381e7da00f","tid":2399614,"uid":54800,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T09:38:49.000Z","msg":"第一次聽見有&quot;稅務學會&quot;...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T09:40:40.000Z","msg":"佢哋有個試叫 certified tax advisor"},{"pid":"a3a32dbf9aaedaa8a0524644d945792b8085efe7","tid":2399614,"uid":335434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"84e8ceb404a2fa015c2c9e4341a1ed381e7da00f","tid":2399614,"uid":54800,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T09:38:49.000Z","msg":"第一次聽見有&quot;稅務學會&quot;...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T09:42:30.000Z","msg":"佢地年年財政預算案前都出嚟噏嘢架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b7a18fdd74277dc06fcb8e7856c0579927b4085","tid":2399614,"uid":288675,"l